人太理性"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T15:35:48.000Z","msg":"手足，可唔可以幫手推post?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T16:31:08.000Z","msg":"上個星期我請埋假最後金鐘得廿個人都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}